</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Part of the <a href="/wiki/Eastern_Front_(World_War_II)" title="Eastern Front (World War II)">Eastern Front</a> of <a href="/wiki/World_War_II" title="World War II">World War II</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:German_pows_stalingrad_1943.jpg" class="image" title="German pows stalingrad 1943.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/88/German_pows_stalingrad_1943.jpg/300px-German_pows_stalingrad_1943.jpg" width="300" height="214" border="0" /></a><br />
Soviet soldiers lead German <a href="/wiki/Prisoners_of_war" title="Prisoners of war" class="mw-redirect">POWs</a> past the Stalingrad grain silo in February 1943.</td>
</tr>
