<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Date</th>
<td>July 17, 1942 – 2 February 1943<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Location</th>
