<a href="/w/index.php?title=Don_Front&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Don Front (page does not exist)">Don Front</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/62nd_Army_(Soviet_Union)" title="62nd Army (Soviet Union)">Soviet 62nd Army</a><br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<b>Initial</b>:<br />
187,000 men<br />
2,200 artillery pieces<br />
400 tanks<br />
300 aircraft<sup id="cite_ref-Bergstrom2007_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Bergstrom2007-2" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup><span class="reference plainlinksneverexpand" style="white-space:nowrap"><sup>:72</sup></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<b>At the time of the Soviet counter-offensive</b>: 1,103,000 men<br />
15,501 artillery pieces<br />
1,463 tanks<br />
1,115<sup id="cite_ref-hayward98_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-hayward98-3" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup><span class="reference plainlinksneverexpand" style="white-space:nowrap"><sup>:224</sup></span> aircraft</td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;"><a href="/wiki/Army_Group_B" title="Army Group B">Army Group B</a>:<br />
<a href="/wiki/German_Sixth_Army" title="German Sixth Army" class="mw-redirect">German Sixth Army</a><br />
German Fourth Panzer Army<br />
<a href="/wiki/Romanian_Third_Army" title="Romanian Third Army" class="mw-redirect">Romanian Third Army</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Romanian_Fourth_Army" title="Romanian Fourth Army" class="mw-redirect">Romanian Fourth Army</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Italian_Army_in_Russia" title="Italian Army in Russia">Italian Eighth Army</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Hungarian_Second_Army" title="Hungarian Second Army" class="mw-redirect">Hungarian Second Army</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/369th_Reinforced_Infantry_Regiment" title="369th Reinforced Infantry Regiment">Croatian Legion</a><br />
<br />
<b>Initial</b>:<br />
270,000 men<br />
3,000 artillery pieces<br />
500 tanks<br />
600 aircraft, 1,600 by mid-September (<i><a href="/wiki/Luftflotte_4" title="Luftflotte 4">Luftflotte 4</a></i>)<sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-4" title=""><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-Bergstrom2007_2-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Bergstrom2007-2" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup><span class="reference plainlinksneverexpand" style="white-space:nowrap"><sup>:72</sup></span><br />
<br />
<b>At the time of the Soviet counter-offensive</b>:<br />
1,011,000 men<br />
10,250 artillery pieces<br />
675 tanks<br />
