</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Kotelnikovo_Offensive_Operation&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Kotelnikovo Offensive Operation (page does not exist)">Kotelnikovo Offensive Operation</a> 12 December 1942 - 31 December 1942
<ul>
<li>Stalingrad Front <a href="/wiki/2nd_Guards_Army_(Soviet_Union)" title="2nd Guards Army (Soviet Union)">2nd Guards</a>, <a href="/w/index.php?title=5th_Shock_Army_(Soviet_Union)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="5th Shock Army (Soviet Union) (page does not exist)">5th Shock</a>, 51st, 8th Air Armies</li>
